                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870110-9-defend102 t17870110-9-punish52"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice WILSON.</p>
